text: You come to her with a problem and she fixes it for you. I go to her ever since i was a kid and she never fails to impress me.

My joints pain got worse after seeing this TCM. She didn't even 把脉 and straight concluded my joint pain is due to digestive problems. She even persuaded me to consume her medicine which doesn't help with the pain. Went back to GP and got diagnosed with viral arthritis. Took Naproxen and got better. Please do not make assumptions. Every patient is different.

I'm always thankful for the Sin Seh (医师)in her profession, be it Acupuncture, Gua Sha, consultation in health, she's the right person to look for! Even if you stay far away! Try it and you will be amazed by her healing hands! Ty 医师!
